The paper discusses a webservice that helps track clone relicensing, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also discusses the licensing of software, which falls under the category of programming languages (cs.PL). The study of code snippet migration can also be categorized under cybernetics (cs.CY), cryptography (cs.CR), and information retrieval (cs.IR).
